    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "## Tell a Persuasive Data Story with AI\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to analyze the Lebron James infographic and tell a persuasive data story.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\nDo This:\r\n1. Upload the **PDF file** of the Lebron James infographic from the library.\r\n2. Ask AI Chat one of these questions:\r\n   - *I want to make the story more convincing. What kind of emotional or statistical angle could I add?*\r\n   - *How could someone mislead others using this infographic? What should I watch out for when telling a data story?*",
